    public class SimulatorOracle<I,​D>
extends Object
implements SingleQueryOracle<I,​D>
    A membership oracle backed by an automaton. The automaton must implement the SuffixOutput concept, allowing to identify a suffix part in the output (relative to a prefix/suffix subdivision in the input).

    Implementation note: Under the assumption that read-operations do not alter the internal state of the automaton, this oracle is thread-safe.
